rows.label: qst701903_msg0002
rows.name:
I can't imagine you're just here to
shoot the breeze with me. Busy
people, or so I hear. Got a job for me?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0003
rows.name: Wowee. All the way to Invidia, you say.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0004
rows.name:
Hmm. Nope, that's fine.
I owe you guys, after all.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0005
rows.name:
The old fart and Wotta are also
in your debt, eh?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0006
rows.name:
So the first stop is Aletta, where I have
to pick up some band of misfits
and take them to Invidia.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0007
rows.name:
Then, when they're done with
whatever they have to do, I should
ship them back to Aletta?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0008
rows.name:
Sounds doable. I'll need a day or two
to get everything shipshape, but I can
meet you in Aletta when I'm done.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0101
rows.name: All that for one little girl, huh?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0102
rows.name:
Everyone on board was raring to go.
You've got some good friends, you
know that? Keep 'em close.
